org.zoolu.sip.dialog

Interface SubscriberDialogListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegisterAgent

    public interface SubscriberDialogListener
    A SubscriberDialogListener listens for SubscriberDialog events. It collects all SubscriberDialog callback functions.
